# Default project rules for Codex

1) Entry point
- Read `AGENTS.md` first.
- Then read `./.codex/core/AGENT.md`, `./.codex/core/RULES.md`, and `./.codex/core/CONVENTIONS.md`.

2) Project structure
- Keep project framework files under `./.codex/`:
  - `./.codex/core`
  - `./.codex/skills`
  - `./.codex/snippets`
  - `./.codex/templates`

3) Skills scope
- Source skills live in `./.codex/skills`.
- Installed runtime skills live in `%USERPROFILE%\\.codex\\skills`.

4) Execution discipline
- Propose a plan before implementation.
- Execute in small steps and verify each step.
- If blocked, switch strategy and continue.
